&lt;h2 id=&#34;transport-research-arena-tra&#34;&gt;Transport Research Arena (TRA)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I will be participating in the Transport Research Arena 2024 (TRA2024), the largest European research and innovation conference on transport and mobility. I will be presenting our research titled &amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Improving the planning of future track interventions using digital tools&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo;, which showcases the a part of STABILITY research project. The paper demonstrates how digital tools are to be used for improving the planning of future track interventions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am looking forward to meeting experts from academia and industry and exchanging ideas. I also look forward to closely get to know the latest developments and innovations in the transport sector, as well as expanding my network and exploring new collaboration opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I hope to see you in Dublin!&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
